              "content": "Chinese HR Leave Policy - Bilingual Summary\n===========================================\n\n员工休假管理制度 (Employee Leave Management Policy)\n\nEffective Date: January 1, 2024\n\n1. 年假 (Annual Leave)\n   - Chinese: 工作满1年享有5天年假，满10年享有10天，满20年享有15天\n   - English: 1 year of service: 5 days; 10 years: 10 days; 20 years: 15 days\n\n2. 病假 (Sick Leave)\n   - Chinese: 凭医院证明可申请，每年累计不超过30天\n   - English: Requires medical certificate; maximum 30 days per year\n\n3. 婚假 (Marriage Leave)\n   - Chinese: 3天（晚婚加7天）\n   - English: 3 days (additional 7 days for late marriage)\n\n4. 产假 (Maternity/Paternity Leave)\n   - Chinese: 女员工158天，男员工陪产假15天\n   - English: Female employees: 158 days; Male employees: 15 days paternity leave\n\n5. 丧假 (Bereavement Leave)\n   - Chinese: 直系亲属3天，旁系亲属1天\n   - English: Immediate family: 3 days; Extended family: 1 day\n\n6. 调休 (Time-off in Lieu)\n   - Chinese: 加班可申请等时调休，需在3个月内使用\n   - English: Overtime can be converted to time-off; must be used within 3 months\n\nPolicy Summary:\n- Comprehensive leave system covering various life events\n- Progressive annual leave based on service years\n- Medical documentation required for sick leave\n- Enhanced benefits for late marriage\n- Generous maternity leave (158 days)\n- Bereavement leave distinction between immediate and extended family\n- Overtime compensation through time-off with usage deadline\n\nThis policy ensures employee welfare while maintaining operational efficiency."
